high_descs: turn right and go straight to the wall with the brown shelf
pick up the glass cup on the top shelf
Turn around, make a left and go straight to the sink, then turn right and face the refrigerator
open the refrigerator, place the glass on the top shelf, and close the door for a few seconds before taking the glass back out
make a left, turn right around the center counter top island, and stop in front of the brown shelf
place the glass on the second shelf from the top, in front of the baby bottle
anns.task_desc: Cool the glass from the shelf so you can return it to a lower shelf

high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the shelves.
Pick up the glass from the shelf.
Turn right and walk to the sink, then turn right again and walk to the fridge and face it.
Open the fridge and set the glass in there and close the door, wait a few seconds and take the glass out again.
Turn left and walk to the sink and turn left again and walk back to the shelves.
Set the glass on the second shelf.
anns.task_desc: Chill the glass in the fridge and return it to the shelf.

high_descs: Turn to the right and go straight back to the brown shelf.
Pick up the glass from the brown shelf.
Carry the glass and turn right to go around the island and find the fridge across the room.
Place the glass inside and shut the door. Open the door and take the glass out, then shut the door.
Hold the glass and turn left around the island to go back to the brown shelf.
Place the glass near the bottom of the brown shelf.
anns.task_desc: Chill a glass and put it away on the shelf.
